Package: runaway-guard
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34), libqt6widgets6 (>= 6.2), libqt6network6 (>= 6.2), libsqlite3-0 (>= 3.34)
Maintainer: RunawayGuard Team <runaway-guard@example.com>
Description: Process monitor for detecting runaway processes
 RunawayGuard is a system tray application that monitors running processes
 for anomalies such as high CPU usage, hanging processes, memory leaks,
 and timeouts. It provides desktop notifications and allows users to
 manage problematic processes directly from the GUI.
 .
 Features:
  - Intelligent process monitoring with adaptive sampling
  - Multiple detection modes: CPU, hang, memory leak, timeout
  - Desktop notifications for alerts
  - Whitelist management for trusted processes
  - SQLite database for alert history
  - Unix socket IPC between daemon and GUI
